Interface BasicExecutor

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Component, Executor<BasicExecutor>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultBasicExecutor

    public interface BasicExecutor
extends Executor<BasicExecutor>
    A basic executor. The basic executor implements the base Executor interface. Users should be careful not to overflow the execute queue when using a basic executor.
